{"tid":1601734,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"全職獵人 - 王位繼承篇整理  (更新至390話)","createTime":"2019-09-29T06:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T10:54:16.000Z","uid":253240,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef1961e2c6b0eaa5522a78b45aaafee8254cf75","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"HXH 嘅黑暗大陸篇，世界觀宏大，人物關係複雜，出場角色極之多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟之前做過一個關於HXH王位繼承戰篇既整理，<br />\n而家做左一個更新至390話既版本，會更加全面講下主要人物登上黑鯨號後既動向，<br />\n多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有咩錯漏，歡迎指正。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc47443e171e6a5f0ba3548f839774eed53c857","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EcE1msm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcE1msm.jpg&h=c4600a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先是王子、王妃以及所屬護衛之列表。根據繼承戰規則：<br />\n<br />\n-每名王子只可帶15位隋從登船<br />\n<br />\n-王子私設兵 (白格): 王子直屬之士兵, 一般而言對王子忠誠心最高。<br />\n<br />\n-王妃所屬兵(白格): 王妃之直屬士兵，有部分會被安插於王子的十五人名單內。以直屬士兵人數不足的下位王子居多。根據374話，相對對王妃較為忠誠。<br />\n<br />\n-獵人 古拿比加派 (粉紅格) : 受古拿比加所委託，前題在「協助古拿比加獲取四王子情報」下，保護其所屬王子。以王位繼承戰保持膠著狀態，安全前往新大陸為目標。<br />\n<br />\n-獵人 協專派 (藍格) : 協助比央特及巴利斯頓勇闖黑暗大陸。在到達假想新大陸前，專職保護其所屬王子。<br />\n<br />\n-王妃監視警衛(黃格) : 上位王妃可向每一個下位王妃各派一名監視警衛。例如十四王子之母愛圖為排行第八，因此會被第一至第七王妃各分派一名警衛。王妃監視警衛是在不會威脅到委託人及其王子的安全條件下，保護其監視之王子。<br />\n<br />\n-隨從(紫格): 根據374話, 隨從有分兩類，有兼任士兵的，也有無法戰鬥的人員，申請的隨從人數愈多，可攜帶家具及日用品之行李上限會增加，相反武器份額側會相應減少。<br />\n<br />\n-一王子私設兵 (綠格) : 一王子地位等於軍事最高副顧問，其私設兵有正規國王軍資格。"},{"pid":"870e5577b93114fc1b13f4ab7640e00f340213d7","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQCaZfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQCaZfc.jpg&h=789295d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上是到390話為止，在漫畫中登場過的主要人員名單。<br />\n<br />\n-修巫巫家族(淺黃格) &ndash; 黑幫，後台為三王子。<br />\n-愛依依家族(灰藍格) &ndash; 黑幫，後台為四王子。<br />\n-加夏亞家族(淺綠格) &ndash; 黑幫，後台為四王子。<br />\n<br />\n-幻影旅團(灰格) &ndash; 庫洛洛魯西魯帶領，來自流星街的世界著名盗賊團隊，上船主要目的為捕殺希索加。<br />\n<br />\n-獵人-十二支(粉紅格)- 受V5所託，為制衡比央特及巴利斯頓而前往新大陸。以王位繼承戰保持膠著狀態，安全前往新大陸為目標。<br />\n<br />\n- 探險隊(藍格) &ndash; 比央特受卡金帝國任命為探險隊的隊長，以被囚禁為交換條件，獲得去暗黑大陸的機會。探險隊為比央特及巴利斯頓所組織之隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n-王子受命的準獵人(白格) &ndash; 以準協會成員身份負責居住區周邊安保，實質以保障所屬王子居住區外的勢力為主要任務。"},{"pid":"6f6f1e51b2b028c7dfa6980e8f2ba6c61e71e92d","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"今晚繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d75d6c2abcd1de8b4aaeafc03b8038f61b45227","tid":1601734,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"想問下富奸今年係咪未復過刊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff3c4ab9c8b6685ca928f76ee2f424f5123ecf8","tid":1601734,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d75d6c2abcd1de8b4aaeafc03b8038f61b45227","tid":1601734,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"想問下富奸今年係咪未復過刊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"今年年初好似復過刊"},{"pid":"6e03b00da7c2c1972788652c0d5b037fe9ab0a6d","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff3c4ab9c8b6685ca928f76ee2f424f5123ecf8","tid":1601734,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d75d6c2abcd1de8b4aaeafc03b8038f61b45227","tid":1601734,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"想問下富奸今年係咪未復過刊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"今年年初好似復過刊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"已經係上年既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5358b95594d73522126822bb99aad32a401ba82a","tid":1601734,"uid":49094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:32:50.000Z","msg":"Mh 出左新dlc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560dcff8c076041ce82911d6574915727fd2950d","tid":1601734,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e03b00da7c2c1972788652c0d5b037fe9ab0a6d","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff3c4ab9c8b6685ca928f76ee2f424f5123ecf8","tid":1601734,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d75d6c2abcd1de8b4aaeafc03b8038f61b45227","tid":1601734,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"想問下富奸今年係咪未復過刊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"今年年初好似復過刊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"已經係上年既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"個故事寫到咁大, 依家仲有4份3王子未死"},{"pid":"c02680f69f553b02e0b53967df43786c8586975a","tid":1601734,"uid":253240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8SeGW8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8SeGW8.jpg&h=8116c099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n - 黑鯨1號開出不到兩小時，便發生第一波屠殺事件。14王子的人員被疑似念能力者或念獸襲擊，五位王妃監視軍被抽乾血液至死。<br />\n<br />\n- 協專獵人卡頓受念獸操控，刺殺了一夠隊友及兩位王妃監視軍，自己因而被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n- 兩位隨從因抵受不了精神壓力而選擇離隊。"},{"pid":"a51b6bd62e2ca43c00c96a47eeffdb1bc61f883b","tid":1601734,"uid":293480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a5850a25ca05d9b4ccca6be5770053b6c1fc56","tid":1601734,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n每次復刊已經唔知自己睇緊d咩"},{"pid":"72f26de03f8915206908717318a45b5bf082f898","tid":1601734,"uid":8561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:32:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a9345e7fb2e2b650b800c949b891ac34117fb7f2","tid":1601734,"uid":134774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:35:51.000Z","msg":"你張圖有253個角色 仲未計念獸 癡撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed704060f9bf6e4107aec469b54c0e8792b0d43","tid":1601734,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:41:51.000Z","msg":"多到咁點記"},{"pid":"48e46a3f103c50ee3c4847826eb5cc44a716b5d4","tid":1601734,"uid":149878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T21:04:57.000Z","msg":"見到巴打開post以為富奸又開始畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暗黑大陸個故仔大到完全睇唔明<br />\n十幾個王子又十幾個護衛重要玩心理戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重送埋十二支、黑幫、旅團<br />\n世界最大篇章都唔過份"},{"pid":"1bf2daaa9ce25c7b760a68bebe82763d38dd48bd","tid":1601734,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T21:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a381463f26031c8eb3306b261cf9c0806ded67a1","tid":1601734,"uid":138097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8a5850a25ca05d9b4